""" Assert that interpolated values can be extracted correctly """
config = ConfigParser(
    """
        a = something
        b = {a} else

        [section]
        c = example
        d = {section:c} proven
        """
    )
self.assertEqual(config, {'a': 'something', 'b': 'something else',
    'section': {'c': 'example', 'd': 'example proven'}})
